    "causal_summary": "Feedback & Quality Learning closes the loop between retrieval and ranking by collecting implicit signals from the calling AI and using them to improve future results. The D4 deep-research agent discovered the system is **more mature than expected**: quality gates already exist in `save-quality-gate.ts` (0.4 density, 0.92 dedup, 50 char min), reconsolidation exists in `reconsolidation-bridge.ts` (opt-in, checkpoint-gated), and learned feedback exists in `learned-feedback.ts` with 10 safeguards. The real gap is **signal collection from the calling AI**, not safeguard design.",
